{
  "3056110": {
    "name": "Calm Skies: The Wingsuit Flying Experience",
    "steam_appid": 3056110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/6bb0ec63f4633c03aa1177487fe383fd.avif?t=1757992165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras_big/6bb0ec63f4633c03aa1177487fe383fd.webp?t=1757992165 width=1560 height=203 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We went to the essence of Calm Skies and re-made it from the ground up (the clouds down?) for our major Trailblazer Edition update. In this new edition, you can look forward to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Better Flying</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Power-ups Added</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dashing Mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revamped Terrain Generation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Engaging Obstacle Spawning</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved Models and Lighting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And many more improvements!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Just part of our initiative to bring more free content and updates to Calm Skies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/c0e5e7873412485b8ab5c7f41c739fd1.avif?t=1757992165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras_big/c0e5e7873412485b8ab5c7f41c739fd1.webp?t=1757992165 width=1560 height=203 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill and tranquility of flying in Calm Skies. Perfect your wingsuit skills as you explore diverse biomes, dodge obstacles, and perform daring tricks to complete skill-testing challenges. Customize your character and enjoy a unique blend of excitement and serenity in the skies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/2a2cbc4482c1c75ff7380fc53e2e5236.avif?t=1757992165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras_big/2a2cbc4482c1c75ff7380fc53e2e5236.webp?t=1757992165 width=1560 height=144 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/197edb16105454fbfb51f28b9f1d8c07.poster.avif?t=1757992165\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/197edb16105454fbfb51f28b9f1d8c07.webm?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/197edb16105454fbfb51f28b9f1d8c07.mp4?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the rush of adrenaline as you glide close to the ground and obstacles, perfecting your flight skills to build an impressive high score. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/049455623ccb57ec2432f9e36fbfee4e.avif?t=1757992165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras_big/049455623ccb57ec2432f9e36fbfee4e.webp?t=1757992165 width=1560 height=144 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/f461c16a3ca36304c1aa21722c98b8cb.poster.avif?t=1757992165\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/f461c16a3ca36304c1aa21722c98b8cb.webm?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/f461c16a3ca36304c1aa21722c98b8cb.mp4?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your reflexes and agility as you maneuver around trees, hills, and narrow gaps on your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/db5b0acd1ee8b6a7b100309301bbd274.avif?t=1757992165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras_big/db5b0acd1ee8b6a7b100309301bbd274.webp?t=1757992165 width=1560 height=144 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/9810eacf2de5ccb982073c447d0da2e2.poster.avif?t=1757992165\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/9810eacf2de5ccb982073c447d0da2e2.webm?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/9810eacf2de5ccb982073c447d0da2e2.mp4?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and explore stunning landscapes and biomes, each offering unique challenges and beauty. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/53d5c67334f4404804bdb5ff6a8c4569.avif?t=1757992165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras_big/53d5c67334f4404804bdb5ff6a8c4569.webp?t=1757992165 width=1560 height=203 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/54d363a9c2bd1ff9fa0087e2b4caff89.avif?t=1757992165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras_big/54d363a9c2bd1ff9fa0087e2b4caff89.webp?t=1757992165 width=1560 height=144 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/643d3a4cf00286e513b8e8678a7817f9.poster.avif?t=1757992165\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/643d3a4cf00286e513b8e8678a7817f9.webm?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/643d3a4cf00286e513b8e8678a7817f9.mp4?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your score by performing daring tricks and flying through rings scattered across the skies. Complete engaging challenges that push your flying abilities, and be rewarded with Wings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/17d88112b992425adaa40335319fa7f9.avif?t=1757992165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras_big/17d88112b992425adaa40335319fa7f9.webp?t=1757992165 width=1560 height=144 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/cdb548c8908eb0450680ae328afd67d3.poster.avif?t=1757992165\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/cdb548c8908eb0450680ae328afd67d3.webm?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056110/extras/cdb548c8908eb0450680ae328afd67d3.mp4?t=1757992165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personalize your wingsuit character with a variety of customization options to make your character truly your own. Unlock new customizations as you earn more Wings from challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive flight mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration in diverse biomes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill Testing Challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheat Codes ;) </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're seeking thrilling high-speed challenges or peaceful moments of aerial exploration, Calm Skies offers an unforgettable wingsuit flying experience. Take to the skies and find your calm amidst the clouds!</p>",
